            <div class="section">
                <h2>How It Works</h2>
                <p>The build revolves around a simple but powerful loop:</p>
                <p><strong>1. Generate Fury</strong> via Shouts (Rallying Cry, War Cry, Challenging Shout) and passive generation from Tempered Fury and Prolific Fury.</p>
                <p><strong>2. Slam with HotA</strong> which deals damage that scales with your current Fury thanks to Unbridled Rage. Each hit consumes Fury for massive damage.</p>
                <p><strong>3. Guaranteed Overpower</strong> from Banished Lord's Talisman triggers after spending enough Fury, creating huge burst windows.</p>
                <p><strong>4. Earthquake Chain</strong> - 100,000 Steps auto-casts Ground Stomp while attacking, which spawns Earthquakes. Mantle of Mountain's Fury detonates those Earthquakes on every HotA impact, creating an AoE damage cascade.</p>
